snippet.title: Demolition Derby 3D for Android: Gameplay
snippet.description:
Demolition Derby 3D by Italy Games launches for Android, here's a quick Gameplay video of the game. 

Get it via Play Store for free: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.game.demolitionderby
